#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_surfacetool.rst:19
msgid ""
"The ``SurfaceTool`` is used to construct a :ref:`Mesh <class_Mesh>` by "
"specifying vertex attributes individually. It can be used to construct a "
":ref:`Mesh <class_Mesh>` from a script. All properties except indices "
"need to be added before calling :ref:`add_vertex "
"<class_SurfaceTool_method_add_vertex>`. For example, to add vertex colors"
" and UVs:"
msgstr ""
"``SurfaceTool`` 用于通过分别指定顶点属性，来构造一个 :ref:`Mesh <class_Mesh>`。它可以用来从脚本构造一个 "
":ref:`Mesh <class_Mesh>`。除索引外，所有属性都需要在调用 :ref:`add_vertex "
"<class_SurfaceTool_method_add_vertex>` 之前添加。例如，要添加顶点颜色和UV："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_surfacetool.rst:29
msgid ""
"The above ``SurfaceTool`` now contains one vertex of a triangle which has"
" a UV coordinate and a specified :ref:`Color <class_Color>`. If another "
"vertex were added without calling :ref:`add_uv "
"<class_SurfaceTool_method_add_uv>` or :ref:`add_color "
"<class_SurfaceTool_method_add_color>`, then the last values would be "
"used."
msgstr ""
"上面的 ``SurfaceTool`` 现在包含一个三角形的一个顶点，该三角形具有UV坐标和一个指定的 :ref:`Color "
"<class_Color>`。如果添加了另一个顶点，而没有调用 :ref:`add_uv "
"<class_SurfaceTool_method_add_uv>` 或 :ref:`add_color "
"<class_SurfaceTool_method_add_color>`，则将使用上次的值。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_surfacetool.rst:31
msgid ""
"Vertex attributes must be passed **before** calling :ref:`add_vertex "
"<class_SurfaceTool_method_add_vertex>`. Failure to do so will result in "
"an error when committing the vertex information to a mesh."
msgstr ""
"必须在调用 :ref:`add_vertex <class_SurfaceTool_method_add_vertex>` **之前** "
"传递顶点属性。否则，将顶点信息提交到网格时，会导致错误。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_surfacetool.rst:33
msgid ""
"Additionally, the attributes used before the first vertex is added "
"determine the format of the mesh. For example, if you only add UVs to the"
" first vertex, you cannot add color to any of the subsequent vertices."
msgstr "此外，在添加第一个顶点之前，使用的属性决定了网格的格式。例如，如果仅将UV添加到第一个顶点，则不能将颜色添加到后续任何顶点。"

